### Technical Notes

**Drag Listener Pattern:**
The fix for the map drag conflict introduces a reusable pattern:
1. SortableWidget passes drag listeners to children
2. Widget applies listeners only to header
3. Content remains interactive

This pattern can be used for any widget with interactive content (future calendar drag-drop, etc.).
